    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique must be performed when falling down, or during the downward arc of a jump (any jump down, or the second half of a horizontal jump). Make a single attack against the target that deals normal damage, plus 1d4+1 per 10 ft fallen (maximum 1d4+1 per level or 12d4+12, whichever is lower). This damage is not multiplied on critical hits.<br><br>This attack will not stop your momentum or movement in any way.</p>\n\n\n\n",
